-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-21/unicredit-ceo-profumo-resigns-chairman-rampl-assumes-duties.html
UniCredit SpA’S Chief Executive
Officer Alessandro Profumo resigned, according to a statement
distributed by the Italian exchange today.  Italy’s biggest bank by assets said Chairman Dieter Rampl
will assume CEO duties, according to the statement. The board
gave a mandate to Rampl to find a new CEO in coming weeks, the
statement said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Marco Bertacche at 
 mbertacche@bloomberg.net  